Look, if you look around it won&#39;t take long before you find this type of hate laden speech. It stems from fear and misunderstanding. It is invited by those who seek validation. You can explain to them your ideas till your blue in the face and they still won&#39;t get it.

My point is, don&#39;t try to convince the unconvincible. Seek people of like mind and spiritual nature and you can&#39;t go wrong. I remember reading this blog among others and I have to say, I am not impressed by their logic or argument. Follow your own path.

Regards,

Frank R.

